Winternights

remake by flanders (mysek.de)
original by: Warbeast 
textures by: flanders & Valve

---------------------------------------------------------
It is still one of my favourite custom Map.
I dont know why. Maybe it is so plain?
I tried to keep all the things to oneselfall plainness.
---------------------------------------------------------

Counter-Terrorists: Rescue the hostages. 
Take out the Terrorists without jeopardizing 
the hostages.

Terrorists: Prevent Counter-Terrorist
force from rescuing the hostages.

Other Notes: There are 4 hostages in 
the mission.
